<% provide(:title, 'Help') %>
<h1>Help</h1>
<ul>
	<li>To use this service, one first needs to register for a new account.</li>
	<li>Name, email address and password must be entered. By default only the email address is disclosed to registered users. If you wish other information such as phone number to become visible, tick the appropriate checkbox next to "Public".</li>
	<li>If the "Expertise" box is filled in (each expertise skill separate by a comma),  then you are an <strong>Expert</strong> and your contact details and description of expertise will be shown to all registered users. Otherwise you are a <strong>User</strong> and your details will not be displayed.</li>
	<li>After signing in, the list of Experts and their contact information will be accessible.</li>
	<li>User's profile can be accessed via <em>My profile</em>.</li>
	<li>User can then contact the Expert based on the contact information. User can also click the <em>Send message</em> button to send private messages to the expert through this service.</li>
	<li>Personal information can be updated at <em>Account-Edit profile</em>.</li>
</ul>
